tool_description: Find out how to get anywhere by car, bike, and foot. Calculate distance and travel time, between cities.
name: FROMTO
title: FROMTO

api_list.name: Distance Foot
api_list.description: A route is described of an array of point objects. Each point object is separated by ";" coordinates are separated by a comma, which describes the name of the point.. (City or lat,lng ) Example: paris;43.2961743,5.3699525;lyon
